stories.text:
Features A fast cross-platform ls Supports Beautiful Icons via NerdFont Traverse a deeply nested folder structure easily! Powerful config system which allows you to customize stuff(like opening files in apps) Supports FCD as well! An inbuilt find command which allows searching files by using the Glob pattern Powerful query system which allows you to see what you want Inbuilt support for deleting, copying, pasting files! Provides extra information about files and folders!

So I built this cross platform `ls` just cause I saw so many cool projects made for mac and linux so here is for windows and added a bunch of better stuff(like fcd,in built find, query system and more...!). Made with Nodejs with (P.S. it has ability of classifying folders with various labels like a node project/rust project based on its available contents!)

Check out its docs https://github.com/Borrus-sudo/Zeus for more information! https://twitter.com/ts_gandalf/status/1458017108026032128?s=20 check out the tweet to see zeus in action(the pic is a small demo of what it can do!)

Drop by a star if you love the project!
